\v 6 \add âLeaders from the tribe of\add* YehudahÂŠ106027 approachedÂŠ106024 Yehoshua at GilgalÂŠ106031 and CalebÂŠ106034 (son of YefunnehÂŠ106037 the KenizziteÂŠ106038) saidÂŠ106032 to him, âYou yourself knowÂŠ106040 what YahwehÂŠ106047 told the manÂŠ106051 of GodÂŠ106053 MoshehÂŠ106050 at Kadesh-Barnea aboutÂŠ106056 me and you.\x + \xo 14:6: \xt Num 14:30.\x*
