\v 13 \add âSoÂŠ106215\add* Yehoshua blessedÂŠ106215 Yefunneh'sÂŠ106224 son \add @Caleb\add* andÂŠ106217 gaveÂŠ106217 himÂŠ106215 HebronÂŠ106220 as his inheritanceÂŠ106225.
