\v 1 The block for Yosef'sÂŠ106970 descendantsÂŠ106969\f + \fr 16:1 \ft i.e., the half-tribes of Efrayim and Menashsheh.\f* wentÂŠ106967 from the YordanÂŠ106971 atÂŠ106979 YerichoÂŠ106974 (east of the \add âsprings\add*), through the wildernessÂŠ106976 into the hill countryÂŠ106979 of Beyt-El.
