\v 6 andÂŠ107042 out to the \add âMediterranean\add*. From Mikmetat in the northÂŠ107046, the border wentÂŠ107042 eastwardÂŠ107049 toward TaanatÂŠ107050-ShilohÂŠ107051 thenÂŠ107042 further east to YanoahÂŠ107055.
