\v 7 The borderÂŠ107267 for MenashshehÂŠ107269 went from AsherÂŠ107270 to Mikmetat \add âopposite\add* ShekemÂŠ107276, thenÂŠ107266 went \add âsouthÂŠ107281\add* towards the spring at Tappuah.
