\v 10 \add So\add* the south was for EfrayimÂŠ107321 and the north was for MenashshehÂŠ107323, and the seaÂŠ107325 was the \add western\add* borderÂŠ107326, meeting AsherÂŠ107327 from the north and Yissakar from the east.
