\v 12 \add âButÂŠ107362\add* Menashsheh'sÂŠ107365 descendantsÂŠ107364 weren't able to takeÂŠ107366 possessionÂŠ107366 of those citiesÂŠ107369, \add âso\add* the CanaanitesÂŠ107372 continued to liveÂŠ107373 in the region.\x + \xo 17:12-13: \xt Jdg 1:27-28.\x*
