\v 14 Then the \add two\add* \add âhalf-tribes of Efrayim and Menashsheh\add* asked Yehoshua, âWhy have youÂŠ107400 \add only\add* givenÂŠ107400 to \add #us\add* one measured allocation as an inheritanceÂŠ107402 when \add #we're\add* \add very\add* numerousÂŠ107410 \add because\add* YahwehÂŠ107418 has \add âalready\add* blessedÂŠ107417 \add #us\add*?â
