\v 15 âIf \add âthere's so many of you\add*,â Yehoshua \add âanswered\add*, âand if Efrayim'sÂŠ107444 hill-country is too small for you, goÂŠ107429 into the forestedÂŠ107431 area of the PerizzitesÂŠ107436 and the RefaitesÂŠ107437 and clearÂŠ107432 some landÂŠ107435 for yourselves there.â
