\v 16 âThe hill countryÂŠ107453 \add certainly\add* isn'tÂŠ107449 big enough for \add all of\add* us,â \add *they\add* respondedÂŠ107446, âplusÂŠ107454 the CanaanitesÂŠ107458 living in the YezreelÂŠ107470 valley and in Beyt-Shan and the surrounding towns have iron chariotsÂŠ107454.â
