\v 17 \add âSoÂŠ107472\add* Yehoshua told the \add âhalf-tribes of EfrayimÂŠ107478 and MenashshehÂŠ107479\add*, â\add Yes\add*, there's a lot of you and you're very powerfulÂŠ107485. One land allotment \add âwouldn't be enough for you\add*
\v 18 \add âso\add* the hill countryÂŠ107496 will be yoursÂŠ107506 \add as well\add*. \add âHowever\add*, it's a forestÂŠ107502 and you'll have to clearÂŠ107504 it to the bordersÂŠ107507. You'll \add need to\add* drive out the CanaanitesÂŠ107513 even if they are strongÂŠ107519 and with iron chariotsÂŠ107515.â
