\v 6 You all should write descriptionsÂŠ107612 of the seven parts and bringÂŠ107618 them here to me, and in frontÂŠ107625 of our godÂŠ107627 YahwehÂŠ107626, I'llÂŠ107621 throwÂŠ107621 dice for you \add to allocate them to the seven tribes\add*.
\v 7 However, the LevitesÂŠ107633 don'tÂŠ107630 receive a portionÂŠ107632, becauseÂŠ107635 their inheritance is Yahweh's priesthoodÂŠ107637. GadÂŠ107640 and Reuven and the MenashshehÂŠ107644 half-tribe have \add already\add* receivedÂŠ107645 their inheritance thatÂŠ107650 Yahweh's servantÂŠ107654 MoshehÂŠ107653 allocated to them onÂŠ107634 the easternÂŠ107649 sideÂŠ107647 of the YordanÂŠ107648.
