\v 6 \add âSoÂŠ108731 then that person\add* must stay in the city until they're brought before \add âthe panel of judgesÂŠ108740\add*. \add If they decide that the death wasn't deliberate,\add* the person must remain in that city until the death of the high priestÂŠ108744, then they can \add freely\add* returnÂŠ108752 to their own city andÂŠ108731 own home.â
