\v 1 \add âA long timeÂŠ110516 passed\add* and YahwehÂŠ110522 had givenÂŠ110521 YisraelÂŠ110523 \add âpeace without attacks\add* from theirÂŠ110526 enemiesÂŠ110526 all around, and Yehoshua was \add now\add* \add âin his old age\add*,
